data.description: Come see this entertainer's DREAM HOME!  4856 total square feet with 4186 square feet of updated main house that includes 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bath, including the in-law suite downstairs.  Master suite has generous closets, dual vanity and jacuzzi tub.  In-law suite offers private living space w/ kitchen, fireplace, storage closets, full bath, and bedroom.  POOL HOUSE offers an additional bedroom, bathroom, sitting room and storage attic.  Enjoy the large family room for cozy evenings or the NEW expansive screened in back porch in good weather.  Pool has outdoor shower, gas heated jacuzzi, pergola, TIKI BAR, solar shower and fencing.  All with a VIEW of the Lake and your PRIVATE DOCK.  Enjoy that same view from the updated kitchen complete with WINE FRIDGE.  Have a musician in the family??  Music room is right off the family room!!  There is no shortage of STORAGE with this property.  TWO garages, plus wired workshop and storage building.  Freshly redone circular driveway with classic fountain allows plenty of parking for events or large families that is set well off the road on this large almost 2-acre lot.  NO HOA. Back half of property fenced with classic black iron fencing for kids or dogs.  This property is the perfect blend of classic elements, updated features, spaciousness and endless potential.  ALL REASONABLE OFFERS WILL BE CONSIDERED.
